.SH NAME
.PP
\f[V]ntp-metrics-exporter\f[R] - Prometheus/OpenMetrics exporter for the
ntpd-rs daemon
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
\f[V]ntp-metrics-exporter\f[R] [\f[V]-c\f[R] \f[I]path\f[R]]
